            <span>Open a <strong class="text-zec-text">terminal</strong> — press <kbd class="text-[11px] bg-zec-dark border border-zec-border rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-zec-text font-sans">Ctrl+Alt+T</kbd></span>
